    "parent": "sapphire_proces_container",
    "children": [],
    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- HOW SAPPHIRE WORKS SECTION -->\n<section class=\"sapphire-proces-section\">\n  <div class=\"sapphire-proces-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n      <span class=\"mh-badge\">PROCESS</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">How does Sapphire FUE work?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-description\">The Sapphire FUE transplant process takes place in several steps that ensure maximum precision and natural results.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"proces-layout\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-column\">\n        <h3 class=\"timeline-title\">5 steps of the Sapphire FUE Method</h3>\n        <div class=\"timeline\">\n          <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"timeline-number\">1</div>\n            <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n              <h4>Graft extraction</h4>\n              <p>Hair follicular units are extracted from the donor area (most commonly the back of the head) using micro-surgical instruments. Each graft contains 1 to 4 hairs.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"timeline-number\">2</div>\n            <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n              <h4>Graft sorting</h4>\n              <p>Extracted grafts are carefully sorted by hair count to achieve the most natural result possible. Single-hair grafts are primarily used to create the front hairline, while multi-hair grafts are implanted into other areas to achieve optimal density.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"timeline-number\">3</div>\n            <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n              <h4>Creating micro-channels</h4>\n              <p>The doctor uses the sapphire blade to create micro-channels in the transplant area. These determine the future depth, angle, and direction of hair growth. They allow precise planning of density and overall graft distribution.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"timeline-number\">4</div>\n            <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n              <h4>Graft implantation</h4>\n              <p>Sorted grafts are then carefully placed into the pre-created micro-channels. Thanks to this systematic preparation, it is possible to efficiently work with a higher number of grafts and ensure even, natural coverage of the transplanted area.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"timeline-number\">5</div>\n            <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n              <h4>Healing and growth</h4>\n              <p>The healing phase follows the procedure. During the first weeks, transplanted hair may naturally shed (known as shock loss). New hair begins to grow after 3-4 months, and full results are visible after 12-18 months.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"video-column\">\n        <div class=\"video-wrapper\">\n          <video controls class=\"sapphire-video\">\n            <source src=\"https://maxhair.cz/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/FUE_web.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\">\n            <source src=\"https://maxhair.cz/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/FUE_web.mov\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n            Your browser does not support the video tag.\n          </video>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"video-caption\">Video demonstration of Sapphire FUE transplantation using the sapphire blade</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .sapphire-proces-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n  }\n\n  .sapphire-proces-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .proces-layout {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px);\n    margin-top: 60px;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-column {\n    padding-right: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);\n    border-right: 2px solid var(--medium-gray);\n  }\n\n  .timeline-title {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px) 0;\n  }\n\n  .timeline {\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-item {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: clamp(16px, 2vw, 24px);\n    margin-bottom: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);\n    align-items: flex-start;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-item:last-child {\n    margin-bottom: 0;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-number {\n    width: clamp(40px, 5vw, 50px);\n    height: clamp(40px, 5vw, 50px);\n    background: var(--primary-gold);\n    color: var(--black);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-content {\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-content h4 {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 18px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 clamp(8px, 1vw, 10px) 0;\n  }\n\n  .timeline-content p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.6vw, 14px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .video-column {\n    padding-left: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  .video-wrapper {\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */\n    border-radius: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n    margin-bottom: clamp(16px, 2vw, 24px);\n    background: #000;\n  }\n\n  .sapphire-video {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  .video-caption {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 14px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.6;\n    margin: 0;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 992px) {\n    .proces-layout {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px);\n    }\n\n    .timeline-column {\n      padding-right: 0;\n      border-right: none;\n      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--medium-gray);\n      padding-bottom: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);\n    }\n\n    .video-column {\n      padding-left: 0;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .sapphire-proces-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .timeline-item {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 16px);\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
